Class PrimitiveDoubleConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.caelum.vraptor.converter.PrimitiveDoubleConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Converter<java.lang.Double>

    @RequestScoped
public class PrimitiveDoubleConverter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Converter<java.lang.Double>
    Localized version of VRaptor's Double converter. If the input value if empty or a null string, null value is returned. If the input string is not a number a ConversionException will be throw.
